---
title: One-Pot Indian Beef & Potato Curry with Flatbreads & Parsley
description: This aromatic dish features tender beef and hearty potatoes simmered in a rich, flavourful sauce bursting with exotic spices. Each spoonful delivers a perfect balance of heat and warmth, making it an irresistible comfort food.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a89e576959dc8b94ffabf6-d2cf186b.jpeg
